description:
M.I.D (Mixrace In Disguise) AKA DJ Trax + Paradox - Dreams Revisisted is a 95 remix of Brown and Dangerman`s (Also Mixrace) Dreams from 1994. The original version is pretty much all 8 bit. We wanted to remake the track once we had 16 bit Equiptment :)
